### Test API Endpoints
### Use REST Client extension in VS Code or import to Postman

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/api/health

###

### Submit Contact Form
POST http://localhost:5000/api/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "description": "I'm interested in learning more about The Accelerator Bridge program. Can you provide more information about the application process?"
}

###

### Get All Contact Forms (Admin)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/contact

###

### Submit Partnership Form (without file)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/partnership
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "organizationName": "Tech Innovators Inc",
  "contactPersonName": "Jane Smith",
  "email": "jane.smith@techinnovators.com",
  "phoneNumber": "+254 712 345 678",
  "organizationDescription": "We are a leading technology company specializing in AI and machine learning solutions. We have been in business for 10 years and work with Fortune 500 companies.",
  "partnershipDescription": "We would like to sponsor the program and provide mentorship to participants in the Machine Learning track. We can also offer internship opportunities to top performers.",
  "additionalInfo": "We have a team of 5 senior engineers who are willing to volunteer as mentors."
}

###

### Get All Partnership Forms (Admin)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/partnership

